      "role": "user",
      "content": "cool. can u focus the guide on why the change is good for them, but also maybe list a few things they might notice are different? like, if there are specific ways u handle their high-end requests or personal preferences that they might miss if the new system is just \"faster\" but less... refined? just want to be transparent so they don't feel like the service is getting worse.",
